{"tid":310022,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)普羅咪收屍1-2","createTime":"2017-07-05T13:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T16:21:06.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee33cd881981858225e72a7a5f40bd2b19b75192","tid":310022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN64zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7baaf7aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN64zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ed95ba33\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN64zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=80aea1ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/Prometheusposterfixed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2FPrometheusposterfixed.jpg&h=03aeccd0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/48/Alien_Covenant_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F48%2FAlien_Covenant_Poster.jpg&h=33d9c279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一艘懸停的飛船離開了一個看起來與地球有些相似的星球，留在地表的一位類人類外星人看著離開的飛船，開啟一瓶黑色、冒泡的液體喝下，然後他的身體立即就開始瓦解。外星人的遺體分化後進入旁邊的瀑布，他的DNA引發了生源反應。<br />\n2089年，考古學家伊莉莎白&middot;蕭（Elizabeth Shaw）與查理&middot;哈洛維（Charlie Holloway）在蘇格蘭的斯凱島找到了一份星圖，這份星圖與其他幾個相互間沒有聯繫的古文明遺蹟中找到的相符。他們相信，這是由人類的先驅「工程師」所發出的邀請。韋蘭公司的年邁的執行長彼得&middot;韋蘭（Peter Weyland）為一支探險隊提供資金，讓他們登上科研飛船「普羅米修斯號」根據星圖前往遙遠的行星LV-223。飛船飛行過程中船員都處於休眠狀態，由人形機器人大衛（David）對旅程加以監控。船隻於2093年到達目的地，船員得知他們的任務是要找到工程師。此次任務的負責人梅莉迪絲&middot;維克斯（Meredith Vickers）命令船員沒有她的允許不能擅自與外星生命接觸..<br />\n<br />\n2.2104年，開往銀河系另一端遙遠星球的殖民太空船「聖約號」在前往預定的星球時發生小意外而故障，維修其間船員收到來自附近一個未知星球的神秘信號，於是船長決定前往追蹤這個信號的來源地，不幸地這裡其實是一個布滿黑暗和危險的世界..<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *聲稱話唔係異形既異形電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456e6fcf514bc9cd34ff4e03e833b9a4612bb9c0","tid":310022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d5e5b4ea0964f76990529d5098e8b1565e8392","tid":310022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b52b7f27c5e021117735821b4ba6ba4a7f8974","tid":310022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb1a68df0f820911f41b101d9cc45d92570d76d","tid":310022,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}